Lines.Comment: One day, young sorceress, you will be the greatest mage of all.
It's been a while, young sorceress. And yet I know I can still rely on you.
And I could say the same about you.
Be warned, human. I am NOTHING like Thrall!
Silence. There is a battle to be one.
Silence. There is a battle to be one.
Antonidus's lapdog. How is he by the way? (dark)Still dead?
Jaina, the Lich King still offers you a place by his side...
Come, we will destroy them together!
End your prattle. We have a battle to win.
